## Smart Telescope

### Overview
This app transforms your stargazing experience by leveraging GPS and sensor data to help you locate and observe celestial objects. Simply choose your telescope mount, and the app will guide you through the process of finding and viewing stars and planets.
The real-time data display and BLE communication ensure accurate and up-to-date information.

### Features
- **User-Friendly Interface:** Simple steps to get started with stargazing.
- **Customizable Telescope Mounts:** Adjust settings based on your equipment.
- **Real-Time Data:** Continuous updates on observable objects.


